<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <% include 'head.ect' %>
        <script type="module" charset="utf-8" src="/util.js"></script>
        <script type="module" charset="utf-8" src="/dialogs.js"></script>
        <script type="module" charset="utf-8" src="/auth_basic_login.js"></script>
        <title>DataFed Login</title>
        <script type="application/json" id="template_data">
        {
            "test_mode" : "<%- @test_mode %>"
        }
        </script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="col-flex ui-widget-content" style="height:100%;border:none">
            <div class="ui-widget-header" style="border:none;flex:none;padding:0.2em .5em">
                <span class='ui-icon ui-icon-box' style='vertical-align:middle;color:white;font-size:1.6em'></span>
                <span style="font-size:1.8em;vertical-align:middle">&nbsp;DataFed - A Scientific Data Federation</span>
                <span id='test_mode' class='ui-state-error' style='display:none'>&nbsp;TEST MODE&nbsp;</span>
                <div style='float:right;padding:.2em 0 0 0'>
                    <button class="btn btn-help">Help</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="flex:auto;overflow:auto">
            <div style="font-size:110%;text-align:justify;text-justify: inter-word;margin:3em auto 1em auto;width:35em">
                <div style='font-size:225%'>DataFed Log In / Registration</div>
                <hr>
                <div style='font-size:80%'>Version <%- @version %></div>
                <h2>Log-In</h2>
                <p>To log-in to an existing account, enter DataFed user ID and DataFed password, then click the "Log In"
                button. The DataFed password can be changed by accessing the settings dialog from the main DataFed window.</p>
                <br>
                <table class="center">
                    <tr><td>User ID:</td><td><input type="text" id="input1-uid"></input></td></tr>
                    <tr><td>Password:</td><td><input type="password" id="input1-pw"></input></td></tr>
                </table>
                <br><br>
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <button class="btn btn-login">Log In</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-cancel">Cancel</button>
                </div>
                <br>
                <h2>Registration</h2>
                <p>To register a new user, enter the new user ID, password, and password verification, then click the
                "Register" button. This will create a new user and set the password. If a user with the same ID exists,
                registration will fail.</p>
                <br>
                <table class="center">
                    <tr><td>User ID:</td><td><input type="text" id="input2-uid"></input></td></tr>
                    <tr><td>Name:</td><td><input type="text" id="input2-name"></input></td></tr>
                    <tr><td>Password:</td><td><input type="password" id="input2-pw"></input></td></tr>
                    <tr><td>(verify):</td><td><input type="password" id="input2-pw-verify"></input></td></tr>
                </table>
                <br><br>
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <button class="btn btn-register">Register</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-cancel">Cancel</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ui-widget-header" style="flex:none;padding:.25em">
                <div style='padding:0.5em 1em'>
                    <div class='row-flex'>
                        <div style='flex:none'><span class='ui-icon ui-icon-alert'></span></div>
                        <div style='flex:1 1 auto;padding-left:0.5em'>DataFed is for open data, fundamental research and/or open-source applications
                        and does not meet requirements for protecting HIPPA/ITAR, sensitive, proprietary
                        or other controlled unclassified information.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div id='msg_daily_div' class='row-flex' style='display:none;padding-top:1em'>
                        <div style='flex:none'><span class='ui-icon ui-icon-alert'></span></div>
                        <div id='msg_daily' style='flex:1 1 auto;padding-left:0.5em'></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
